The paper deals with deterministic sketching and streaming algorithms for sparse recovery and norm estimation, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT), data structures (cs.DS), machine learning (cs.LG), numerical analysis (cs.NA), and computational complexity (cs.CC). The paper also mentions the Fast Johnson-Lindenstrauss transform, which is a well-known technique in computer science and machine learning.
